  "texts": [
    "Given that LLMs are trained on human text, it's not surprising that they could be biased toward selecting certain words.",
    "Word+Review used 111 of the 118 words.",
    "The top five word choices were: Confusing: 53, Frustrating: 35, Empowering: 33, Valuable: 25, and Effective: 24.",
    "The approach also incorrectly generated two words (Unhelpful, Inspirational) not found in the supplied word list.",
    "In the first instance, gpt-4o-mini selected 'Unhelpful' in response to a target sentiment of 0.1 and with no negative words in the list of 10 PDT words."
  ],
